Date:   Wed Oct 8 11:33:50 2014 +0300

    lib-storage: Fixed earlier LAYOUT=index change to refresh index before opening a view to it.
    Fixes an assert-crash.

commit 6ae7a38d1f2ac93e2ba17937bd3061e4d8eb23c8
