Date:   Tue Jul 29 14:25:13 2014 +0300

    libressl fix: Check for SSL_CTRL_SET_ECDH_AUTO macro instead of OpenSSL version number
    Patch by Hanno Böck

commit 003385823ea4d859b778f41de18aac8405a00818
