Date:   Thu Sep 26 05:51:43 2013 +0200

    Panic if io_remove() fails with EBADF.
    It's a bug that shouldn't really be ignored. Panicing will give a debuggable
    core dump.

commit fe145bd9fbeb609a691e23998117d62f40a3d00c
