Author: Timo Sirainen <tss@iki.fi>
Date:   Tue Feb 26 09:05:09 2013 +0200

    scram-sha1: Support authzid field. Check fields' correctness better.

commit f888f3029cf6418e34b21aace98cd1086c3f11b4
Author: Timo Sirainen <tss@iki.fi>
