commit 65c0e43da8cfc730eeb4634f8aa384081bbfa4e7
Author: Timo Sirainen <tss@iki.fi>
Date:   Mon Jan 7 12:24:29 2013 +0200

    lib-http: Various fixes
    Patch by Stephan Bosch.

