Date:   Mon Nov 5 14:27:52 2012 +0200

    lib-ssl-iostream: [io]streams were added an unnecessary reference, causing memory leaks.

commit c01803010e0f00b04f2234a494c877e3af7da9fc
Author: Timo Sirainen <tss@iki.fi>
